{"type":"text","timestamp":1778467610450,"sessionID":"ses_1eb192b47ffetNAoTve2ULg7cC","part":{"id":"prt_e14ee0397002F9yzHYD1qW14RP","messageID":"msg_e14edca3100179ZIw1KSQhcaF0","sessionID":"ses_1eb192b47ffetNAoTve2ULg7cC","type":"text","text":"All tasks for issue #31051 are complete.\n\n**What was done:**\n1. Renamed three GO terms from \", sensu Metazoa\" to \"animal\" per @pgaudet's request for consistency with GO naming conventions:\n   - GO:0045136 → `development of animal secondary sexual characteristics`\n   - GO:0046543 → `development of animal secondary female sexual characteristics`\n   - GO:0046544 → `development of animal secondary male sexual characteristics`\n2. Preserved original labels as EXACT synonyms and the intermediate \"sensu Metazoa\" labels as RELATED synonyms.\n3. Updated the `is_a` comment label in GO:0042695 (thelarche) to match the new parent name.\n4. Updated the taxon constraint label in `src/taxon_constraints/only_in_taxon.tsv`.\n5. Validated OBO syntax with `robot convert` (passes cleanly).\n6. Committed only the two files I edited: `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` and `src/taxon_constraints/only_in_taxon.tsv`.\n\n**Output files created (not committed):**\n- `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` — brief status update for the issue thread\n- `PR_COMMENTS.md` — detailed PR description with rationale and checklist\n\nLet me know if you need anything else!","time":{"start":1778467603351,"end":1778467610448}}}
